message.text:
𝐇𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩 𝐤𝐚 𝐧𝐚 𝐧𝐢 𝐊𝐢𝐚𝐧 👀

Kahit saan ka man tumingin o pumunta, may OTreas kang makikita. Mga feeling Dora na everything, everywhere, all at once, nandoon kami! Kaya hinding-hindi ka talaga magsasawa sa PsychSoc OTreas.

At dahil dyan, apply na kayo sa office namin!

You can join the Logistics Department or the Finance and Sponsorship Department. Ikaw na bahala basta sure kami hindi ka magsasawa sa department mo.

See you in Otreas PsychTams! 

Application link:

https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership

message.text:
𝐇𝐢𝐧𝐚𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩 𝐤𝐚 𝐧𝐚 𝐧𝐢 𝐊𝐢𝐚𝐧 👀

Kahit saan ka man tumingin o pumunta, may OTreas kang makikita. Mga feeling Dora na everything, everywhere, all at once, nandoon kami! Kaya hinding-hindi ka talaga magsasawa sa PsychSoc OTreas.

At dahil dyan, apply na kayo sa office namin!

You can join the Logistics Department or the Finance and Sponsorship Department. Ikaw na bahala basta sure kami hindi ka magsasawa sa department mo.

See you in Otreas PsychTams! 

Application link:

https://bit.ly/FEUPsychologySociety_Membership
